FBIS4-50780 "drchi099_e_94003" FBIS-CHI-94-099 Daily Report 20 May 1994 Southeast Asia & Pacific NPC Vice Chairman Ni Zhifu Meets Laotian Guests NPC Vice Chairman Ni Zhifu Meets Laotian Guests OW2005125994 Beijing XINHUA in English 1246 GMT 20 May 94 OW2005125994 Beijing XINHUA English BFN [Text] Beijing, May 20 (XINHUA) -- Ni Zhifu, vice-chairman of the Standing Committee of China's National People's Congress (NPC), hosted a dinner here today for a delegation from the Lao Federation of Trade Unions. They exchanged opinions on issues of common interest. The four-member delegation, headed by the federation's president, Khampan Philavon, started a five-day goodwill visit to China yesterday at the invitation of the All-China Federation of Trade Unions.
